import numpy as np

def extract_array(matrix):
    for i in matrix:
        print(i)
    print("--------------------------------------")
    l = 3
    w = len(matrix)
    for n in range(l):
        if n < (l-1):
            str1 = ''.join(str(i) for i in matrix[n])
            str2 = ''.join(str(i) for i in matrix[n+1])
            str3 = ''.join(str(i) for i in matrix[n+2])
            str4 = str1[0] + str2[1:w-1] + str3[w-1]
        else:
            str4 = ''.join(str(i) for i in matrix[l-1])
        print(str4)
        print("--------------------------------------")
